    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade masterpiece that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and ultraviolet exposure since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring deep, mirror-like paint clarity with a professional-grade ceramic coating and absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent still lingers. All technological features, from the infotainment system to the climate control, function with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every oil change and fluid flush performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage remains free of any debris or oxidation. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
